<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 09:14:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>西门子能源首席执行官呼吁亚洲风电公司进入欧洲进行公平竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/siemens-energy-ceo-calls-fair-competition-asian-wind-firms-enter-europe-2024-08-07/</link><description>西门子能源首席执行官周三表示，活跃在欧洲的中国和西方风力涡轮机制造商必须在相同的市场条件下销售产品，以创造公平竞争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 07:45:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/siemens-energy-ceo-calls-fair-competition-asian-wind-firms-enter-europe-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>投资者在中国针对恒大集团提出清算申请</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investor-files-liquidation-petition-china-against-evergrande-unit-2024-08-07/</link><description>据请愿者周三提交的一份股票文件显示，一名投资者已向中国法院提交请愿，要求清算负债累累的房地产开发商中国恒大的一个主要部门。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 07:12:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investor-files-liquidation-petition-china-against-evergrande-unit-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>投资者称恒大集团在中国提交清算申请</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investor-says-files-liquidation-petition-china-against-evergrande-unit-2024-08-07/</link><description>据请愿者周三提交的一份股票文件显示，一名投资者已向中国法院提交请愿，要求清算负债累累的房地产开发商中国恒大的一个主要部门。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:42:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/investor-says-files-liquidation-petition-china-against-evergrande-unit-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>德国6月出口降幅超预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-exports-fall-more-than-forecast-june-2024-08-07/</link><description>周三官方数据显示，由于该国主要贸易伙伴美国和欧盟其他国家的需求疲软，德国六月份出口降幅超出预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:23:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-exports-fall-more-than-forecast-june-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>拜尔斯道夫未达到利润预期，称中国经济放缓影响了奢侈品牌销售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/nivea-maker-beiersdorfs-sales-grow-despite-china-weakness-2024-08-07/</link><description>妮维雅 (Nivea) 制造商拜尔斯道夫 (Beiersdorf) 周三公布的半年营业利润未达预期，并表示中国奢侈品市场放缓影响了其莱珀妮 (La Prairie) 品牌的销售。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 06:03:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/nivea-maker-beiersdorfs-sales-grow-despite-china-weakness-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国在南海黄岩岛附近举行联合作战巡逻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-holds-joint-combat-patrol-near-scarborough-shoal-south-china-sea-2024-08-07/</link><description>南部战区在微信应用程序上发帖称，中国军队周三在南海黄岩岛附近组织海空联合作战巡逻。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 04:45:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-holds-joint-combat-patrol-near-scarborough-shoal-south-china-sea-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日本央行拯救了局面</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-07/</link><description>Stella Qiu 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 04:38:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>新加坡星展银行上调 2024 年预期，因强劲的财富流动推动利润增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/singapores-bank-dbs-second-quarter-net-profit-rises-4-beats-forecast-2024-08-07/</link><description>新加坡最大的银行星展集团受益于蓬勃发展的财富业务，将资产和费用收入推至创纪录水平，周三，星展集团上调了全年利润指引。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 04:13:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/singapores-bank-dbs-second-quarter-net-profit-rises-4-beats-forecast-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国进口恢复增长但出口放缓引发前景担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-growth-slows-3-month-low-july-imports-up-solidly-2024-08-07/</link><description>7月份，中国的出口增长速度为三个月来最慢，低于预期，加剧了人们对庞大制造业前景的担忧，而在美国预期的科技限制措施之前急于增加芯片供应，导致进口增加。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:52:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-growth-slows-3-month-low-july-imports-up-solidly-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾、美国、澳大利亚、加拿大将在南海举行首次联合演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-us-australia-canada-hold-first-joint-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-08-07/</link><description>菲律宾、加拿大、美国和澳大利亚四国军方表示，周三在南海举行了首次联合军事演习，以加强两国军队之间的互操作性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:34:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-us-australia-canada-hold-first-joint-exercises-south-china-sea-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>据英国《金融时报》报道，中国恒大清算人对普华永道提起法律诉讼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-evergrandes-liquidators-initiate-legal-action-against-pwc-ft-reports-2024-08-07/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》周二报道，陷入困境的房地产巨头中国恒大集团的清算人已对普华永道采取法律行动，指责其在为集团工作时“疏忽”和“失实陈述”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 02:46:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-evergrandes-liquidators-initiate-legal-action-against-pwc-ft-reports-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>Shabab Al-Ahli 在亚洲冠军联赛精英赛中发起了 Al-Gharafa 冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/shabab-al-ahli-set-up-al-gharafa-clash-asian-champions-league-elite-2024-08-07/</link><description>阿拉伯联合酋长国的沙巴布·阿赫利在伊斯法罕加时赛中以 4-1 的比分战胜伊朗东道主塞帕汉，下周将迎战卡塔尔的阿尔加拉法，争夺新一届亚洲冠军联赛精英赛的小组赛席位。周二。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 00:55:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/shabab-al-ahli-set-up-al-gharafa-clash-asian-champions-league-elite-2024-08-07/</guid></item><item><title>面对中国的“胁迫”，美国将增加澳大利亚的兵力投送</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-us-discuss-greater-defence-cooperation-2024-08-06/</link><description>两国在年度防务会谈后表示，澳大利亚将于明年开始与美国共同制造制导武器，以增加对印太地区盟国的供应，并增加美国在该国的军事存在，包括轰炸机。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 22:14:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-us-discuss-greater-defence-cooperation-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国需求改善，Vans 母公司 VF Corp 第一季度营收降幅小于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/vans-parent-vf-corp-posts-smaller-q1-revenue-drop-than-expected-better-china-2024-08-06/</link><description>VF Corp 周二公布，由于中国业务改善以及库存水平下降，第一季度营收降幅小于预期，导致其股价在盘后交易中上涨约 7%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 21:42:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/vans-parent-vf-corp-posts-smaller-q1-revenue-drop-than-expected-better-china-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国学者在美充当外国代理人被判刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/chinese-academic-convicted-acting-foreign-agent-us-2024-08-06/</link><description>周二，一名中国学者被判在美国非法充当外国代理人，他收集了纽约支持中国民主的活动人士的信息，并与北京分享了他的调查结果。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 17:13:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/chinese-academic-convicted-acting-foreign-agent-us-2024-08-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>